mono-tools
------------------------------------------
Collection of tools for the Mono CSharp environment:
* gasnview - ASN.1 viewer
* gendarme - rule-based tool to find problems .NET assemblies
* gnunit   - NUnit framework GUI
* monodoc  - documentation viewer and monodoc tools wrapper

Runtime requirements:
  gconf-sharp2-2.20.1-1
  glade-sharp2-2.12.1-1
  glib-sharp2-2.12.1-1
  gnome-sharp2-2.20.1-1
  gtk-sharp2-2.12.1-1
  gtkhtml-sharp-2.20.1-1
  mono-2.0-1
  monodoc-2.0-1
  webkit-sharp-0.3.105827-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf2.5-2.63-1
  automake1.10-1.10.1-1
  cygport-0.4.0-1
  gawk-3.1.6-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  make-3.81-1
  pkg-config-0.23a-2
  sed-4.1.5-2

Canonical website:
  http://www.mono-project.com/

Canonical download:
  http://go-mono.com/sources-latest/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack mono-tools-2.0-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./mono-tools-2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/mono-tools-2.0-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/mono-tools-2.0-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

